name: Ego 2015 : 365 NFT morphing
description: I made this video with the 365 photos of the lints I found in my belly button every day of the year 2015. Each of them has been pinned on a butterfly board as seen on my website ego.center. It's time to drop Navel Fluff Tokens (NFT) : I'll mint one of them for each edition of this video that will be collected.
